<div class="header">
  <h1>Bloodstream</h1>
  <h4>Live longer. Together.</h4>
</div>

<% if signed_in? %>
	<% if current_user.admin? %>
		<%= link_to 'SOS', send_sms_path %>
	<% end %>
<% end %>


<div class="our_mission mt-5 mb-5 ml-5 pl-4 mr-5 pr-4">
	<h1>Our Mission</h1>
	<p>Bloodstream is the lifeline of those who face life's cruel uncertainties. We aim to save the lives of the young and old by raising awareness on the importance of blood donation. We do this through increasing public understanding of the impact of blood donation and supporting programs that drive participation.</p>
	<div class="learn-more-button">
		<%= link_to "Learn More", about_path, id: 'sign-up' %>
		</div>
	</p>
</div>

<div id= "numbers">
<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm">
    	<h1>1</h1>
			<p>person's donation of blood can save three lives.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm">
    	<h1>2,000</h1>
			<p>bags of blood are needed daily in Malaysia. This is excluding emergency cases.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm">
      <h1>2.2%</h1>
			<p>of the Malaysian population are blood donors. This is low compared to 3.5% in developed countries.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm">
			<h1>30 to 45</h1>
			<p>minutes is all it takes to donate. Each person can donate blood once in 3 months.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

